name: FreshCuts Logo
description:
(Click the image to enlarge)

MichelleKathryn PRE-MADE LOGO!

Make this individually designed logo your own, with your company name and colors. (Don't worry, this will only be sold once!) 

HERE'S THE PROCESS: 

1. Select the logo that you want to be yours. Once purchased, your logo will never be sold again. 

2. email info@michellekathryn.com with  
YOUR COMPANY NAME 
 YOUR COLORS (exact colors if you have them)

3. Receive a proof of your logo within 48 hours (sometimes longer on the weekends/holidays) 

4. Once you decide you love it, you'll get the following Hi-Res file types sent to the email address you provide:  

• EPS - 300 dpi High resolution vector file for professional printing 
• JPG - 300 dpi High resolution file for screen based uses (e.g. websites and presentations) 
• PNG - Transparency for use in PowerPoint and websites 

OTHER INFO: 
 
Company names shown are for presentation only and are not available for use. 

All logo designs shown are copyright by MichelleKathryn, and may not be used, copied, recreated or manipulated in any way until purchased.

If you purchase a logo and do not send your information, you won't get your logo.

Any revisions in addition to the name and (1) color change are an additional 50.00 USD.

We also offer custom design services. If you're interested, please email info@michellekathryn.com for pricing and other info.

Thank you!
